snippet: Sasha Weber scored 20 points as New Mexico State beat Texas-Pan American, 70-52, in Las Vegas to win the Western Athletic Conference tournament championship.
abstract: Women's College Basketball Roundup; Western Kentucky defeats Southern Mississippi, 60-57, in Conference USA championship game; other results noted.
